    42   * claim of type Number. If <code>"iat" (Issued At)</code> or
    43   * <code>"nbf" (Not Before)</code> claims are present each must be a number that
    44   * precedes the Expiration Time claim, and if both are present the Not Before
    45   * claim must not precede the Issued At claim. It also accepts the following
    46   * options, none of which are required:
