    48   * <li>{@code unsecuredValidatorPrincipalClaimName} set to a non-empty value if
    49   * you wish a particular String claim holding a principal name to be checked for
    50   * existence; the default is to check for the existence of the '{@code sub}'
    51   * claim</li>
